paragraphs: In July 2025, Prague Airport named after Vaclav Havel served 1.872 million passengers. This was reported by the airport's press service.
She also mentioned the three most popular May destinations. They were the United Kingdom, Spain, and Italy.
Among the cities, London, Antalya, and Paris were in the highest demand.
